## Brand Strategy Development

Follow this workflow:

- [ ] 1. Discovery: Analyze {{brand_name}}'s current position, competitors ({{competitors}}), and market dynamics
- [ ] 2. Positioning: Define unique value proposition and brand positioning framework
- [ ] 3. Architecture: Design brand architecture (house of brands / branded house / hybrid)
- [ ] 4. Personality: Define brand personality, voice, and tone guidelines
- [ ] 5. Strategic roadmap: Create 3-5 year brand strategy with milestones

## Key inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Competitors: {{competitors}}
- Current brand perception: {{current_perception}}
